Description
-----------

Reports OpenGL version, extensions found, rendering paths enabled and
other graphics card related information.

Usage
-----

At the console type...

    gfxinfo

Parameters
----------

This console command does not accept parameters.

Notes
-----

You can use this command to see which rendering paths are potentially
available in your video card for use with the
[r\_renderer](R_renderer_%28cvar%29 "R renderer (cvar)") CVar.

